ticle class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/yql1719661049663.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/yql1719661049663.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"dfb1665702781249\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"dfb1665702781249___abs_252267\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Return the absolute value of a numeric value.</p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"dfb1665702781249__topic_d80276e1_d80277e1_d80278e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"dfb1665702781249__p_d80279e1_d80280e1_d80281e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$abs</span>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">(</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">X</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">)</code>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section p\" id=\"dfb1665702781249__section_w3047ab1b7b5_w3048ab1b7_w3049ab1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"dfb1665702781249__p_d80282e1_d80283e1_d80284e1\">Example: <code class=\"ph codeph\">vResult = $abs(vNum - 100)</code>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"dfb1665702781249__topic_d52817e1_d52818e1_d52819e1_d52820e1_d52821e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d860336e83\">Parameters</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"dfb1665702781249__d6497e20\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">X</var>—numeric value.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"dfb1665702781249__topic_d52822e1_d52823e1_d52824e1_d52825e1_d52826e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d860336e95\">Return Values</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"dfb1665702781249__p_d80294e1_d80295e1_d80296e1\">Absolute value of <var class=\"keyword varname\">X</var>.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"dfb1665702781249__p_d80297e1_d80298e1_d80299e1\">If an error occurs, <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$procerror</span> contains a negative value that identifies the exact error.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"dfb1665702781249__topic_d52827e1_d52828e1_d52829e1_d52830e1_d52831e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d860336e114\">Use</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"dfb1665702781249__p_d80303e1_d80304e1_d80305e1\">Allowed in all component types.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"dfb1665702781249__section_d21_b2y_wbc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d860336e123\">Example: Using <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$abs</span></h2>\n<p class=\"p\">The following example returns the absolute value of the given\n            expression:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"dfb1665702781249__pre_tkg_b2y_wbc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">vResult = $abs(vNumber - 100)\n</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<p class=\"p\">If the value of vNumber is 25, the value stored in vResult is 75.</p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_7424972\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_7424972\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "$abs Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Juni 29, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Return the absolute value of a numeric value. $abs ( X ) Example: vResult = $abs(vNum - 100) Parameters X —numeric value. Return Values Absolute value of X . If an error occurs, $procerror contains a negative value that identifies the exact error. Use Allowed in all component types. Example: Using $abs The following example returns the absolute value of the given expression: vResult = $abs(vNumber - 100) Copy If the value of vNumber is 25, the value stored in vResult is 75. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}